<h2 id="_configuring_the_item_feedback">4. Configuring the item feedback</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Before you can use eKomi, you have to configure the <a href="/en/omni-channel/online-store/extras/customer-feedback">customer feedback</a> menu. Now insert template variables and code into the template <strong>ItemViewSingleItem</strong>. Choose the setting <strong>5</strong> (stars) as the <strong>maximum rating points</strong>.</p>
</div>
